snippet.title: A Floof'sAdventure Trailer
snippet.description:
The giant currant tree has been giving fewer fruits over time, your duty is to, at least, bring back some edible currants to your village...

A Game made by 
Matthis Chenet and Eléonor Thibout
Music by Paul Cuanbinh

School project at Isart Digital
Check out the game on itch io : https://eleonort.itch.io/a-floofs-adventure
---
Feel free to follow me on other social media!
https://anolerabyu.carrd.co/
ArtStation: https://www.artstation.com/anolera

Thank you for watching!
